om/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Mary-In-The-Junkyard.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Mary-In-The-Junkyard.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Mary-In-The-Junkyard.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Mary-In-The-Junkyard.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Mary-in-the-Junkyard">垃圾场的玛丽（Mary）</a>分享了他们怀旧的新单曲“这是我的加利福尼亚”  - 在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mary-in-the-junkyard-this-old-house-ep-review-radar-3756137">玛丽在垃圾桶中 - “这座老房子” EP评论：迷人的艺术流行飙升在炒作上方</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌由Craig Silvey（ <a href="/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a> ， <a href="/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a> ）制作，由Clari Freeman-Taylor，Saya Barbaglia和David Addsion组成，并用Freeman-Taylor的柔软人声和Barbaglia Deep Bass Lines组成。</p><p>在新闻稿中谈到曲目时，乐队分享了：“这是我的加利福尼亚&#39;是一首怀旧歌曲，讲述了我自己的梦想。通过电影和电视看到“加利福尼亚”总是感觉像是一种天堂或成功的想法，并没有真正引起我的共鸣。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="玛丽在垃圾场 - 这是我的加利福尼亚（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9t60aQndiFo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “另外，在这首歌中，有很多关于“抬起你的东西”的歌词 - 长大我，我的朋友会爬上一切，屋顶和树木，也许感觉就像我们在逃脱了我们所处的地方或感到奇怪从高高到高的程度。”</p><p>这首新歌是在今年早些时候发行的首张EP“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mary-in-the-junkyard-this-old-house-ep-review-radar-3756137">This Old House</a> ”之后的。在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mary-in-the-junkyard-this-old-house-ep-review-radar-3756137">EP的四星级评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享了：“他们可能不害怕通过杂草翻阅杂草，但是玛丽在垃圾场的梦幻野心实在太大了您的演讲者和生活。出去，体验这支乐队的肉体，鲜血，胆量和毅力，他们的荣耀和诺言。”</p><p>垃圾场的玛丽还将与<a href="/artists/Sports-Team">运动队</a>一起参加英国巡回赛，并将前往纽约市在大城市举行两次演出，一夜之间支持模特/actriz，以及他们在Baby&#39;s All的首次头条新闻。他们还计划在明年年初在伦敦的面料上玩，标志着他们迄今为止最大的现场表演。在下面查看巡回演出的完整列表，然后访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fmary-in-the-junkyard-tickets%2Fartist%2F5433485" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_6C-W5NJ3m/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541